SYSTEM INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
===========================

1. Set permissions on various files and directories. This must be run as root.

-------- BEGIN SCRIPT -------

chmod 600 @sysconfdir@/choicesocial.php
chown @WWW_USER@:@WWW_USER@ @sysconfdir@/choicesocial.php
install -d @prefix@/var/lib/choicesocial
chown @WWW_USER@:@WWW_USER@ @prefix@/var/lib/choicesocial
chmod 700 @prefix@/var/lib/choicesocial

-------- END SCRIPT -------
